reviews.review_text:
Nice This sounds much better than the SNDBD source of this  show.  Joe really has some fine AUDs up on the Archive.  Check out his recordings of the Spring 87 shows in Philly... they sound so sweet that I had to DL all 3 and make a special 7 disc box set.  Joe, although your recordings don't have many comments, be aware that people are DLing them and groovin just fine.  Keep them comin'.  Great setlists, and the Band is playin' good this night.  

5 stars for show
4 stars for recording
In agreement w/Flyer Yes, there's the rub. I too felt that the SBD lacked a certain Oomph to it. But, I'm one of those maniacs that likes a good AUD over the board everytime. Nice job, taper.
